::Zardus/Mosquitor::

Zardus growls, exiting the ship and looking back at Ocipite 
complaining.

"Neutralize her please, Hurricane. We really don't need her chatter."

He looks ahead at the horizon, watching a shuttle from the Iron Fist 
approaching on the horizon.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Mosquitor follows behind, complaining to himself as he tries to 
reattach his arm.
